{"tid":614113,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"清明節波台船p NBA狗免問","createTime":"2018-04-02T08:45:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-03T02:29:50.000Z","uid":26959,"like":27,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"3546791d7dbc68abb4f03a0e52a9019b65db1d84","tid":614113,"uid":26959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T08:45:30.000Z","msg":"是咁的，黎緊清明節我地唔去拜山了，去船p享受囡囡與海水。  <br />\n我地book 了3 隻船。第一隻 Adela , 租的。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i56.tinypic.com/idwxuv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi56.tinypic.com%2Fidwxuv.jpg&h=315ca61e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i53.tinypic.com/2ldit53.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi53.tinypic.com%2F2ldit53.jpg&h=ebde5b6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n坐50人的，長80幾呎。<br />\n<br />\n另一隻, 私伙的 Princess V62  坐20人 西班牙式遊艇<br />\n<img src=\"http://i54.tinypic.com/snf8zo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi54.tinypic.com%2Fsnf8zo.png&h=b8394965&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i53.tinypic.com/sblb9u.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi53.tinypic.com%2Fsblb9u.png&h=291b1e46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i55.tinypic.com/2iw93x5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi55.tinypic.com%2F2iw93x5.png&h=183cfd08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i56.tinypic.com/zwl47p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi56.tinypic.com%2Fzwl47p.png&h=01d0ddbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i51.tinypic.com/21cgwns.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi51.tinypic.com%2F21cgwns.png&h=cfcd9a8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我中意呢隻多d，入少少，寫意d。<br />\n<br />\n重有一隻普通 中式船。<br />\n<br />\n搞手會買好多果汁同汽水。<br />\n<br />\n4月5號 , 7點西貢碼頭集合<br />\n<br />\n男仔：$1500 位 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （只限波台手腳，本來想搵埋CC台手腳去，不過船家話CC台d鄉下仔有陣味 加錢都唔比上，咁就算了）<br />\n<br />\n女仔：MODEL, 靚女免費。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n普通女仔：唔俾去。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n來吧靚女，識d俾得起$1500去船河的波台手足吧。<br />\n<br />\np.s. 呢d船河無得賺，搞手只求打個和，大家開開心心玩返晚。"},{"pid":"e9d03d0ae2f89044b16dd5c92ca31faeff593fa8","tid":614113,"uid":99364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T08:52:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6ccddf732146be0d61cebd81b399591c89432feb","tid":614113,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T08:54:10.000Z","msg":"我帶女去 打8折ok?"},{"pid":"1034411d4eddf9bbbcd44173b944a121e3b96073","tid":614113,"uid":99364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T08:54:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"123551308a08f912e9d8bb940ea2771e21eecc58","tid":614113,"uid":7090,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T08:54:59.000Z","msg":"想john<br />\n比夠3000你求下你比我john<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c781a51127e766d92d0304505fd578bf1eaaf16e","tid":614113,"uid":26959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ccddf732146be0d61cebd81b399591c89432feb","tid":614113,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T08:54:10.000Z","msg":"我帶女去 打8折ok?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T08:56:41.000Z","msg":"一場手足計平你小小又點話"},{"pid":"9375ea2fe0ca3e06a68ce5ee625c31d6539d1ce5","tid":614113,"uid":26959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"123551308a08f912e9d8bb940ea2771e21eecc58","tid":614113,"uid":7090,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T08:54:59.000Z","msg":"想john<br />\n比夠3000你求下你比我john<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T08:56:53.000Z","msg":"大家開開心心玩返晚吧!"},{"pid":"cc9605c6bd862da2a389f5088e0856765779fd64","tid":614113,"uid":177841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T08:58:09.000Z","msg":